      "message": "yes, but Attempt.StartTime must remain as the time of triggering for backwards compatibility, \nI think you can easily get as \n  r.Trigger.GetTime().AsTime()\n\n(https://source.chromium.org/chromium/infra/infra/+/main:go/src/go.chromium.org/luci/cv/internal/run/storage.proto;l\u003d71;drc\u003dc7f8002e86f514734563172ed66c4236732bfd38)",
